OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud will gradually clear
OL,6,Feastern areas through the morning.
OL,7,FOtherwise, a widely sunny and very
OL,8,Fwarm day with strong sunshine and a
OL,9,Fkeen easterly breeze. Rather windy
OL,10,Falong the south coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine end to the day with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. A few showers may
OL,14,Fpush into southern coastal counties.
OL,15,FLow cloud will build again across the
OL,16,Feast, but clear elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
