OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMostly dry and sunny. Staying
OL,6,Fcloudy around some northeast coasts. A
OL,7,Fchance of showers or thunderstorms in
OL,8,Fthe southwest at first. Very warm with
OL,9,Fa brisk breeze in the south.
